high_descs: Turn to the left, go past the TV to the end of the white shelf.
Pick up the vase that is on the shelf.
Turn around, go to the dining table that is on the left.
Put the vase on the table in front of the statue.
Turn to the right, go forward, Turn to the right, go to the white cabinet just past the shelf with the statue on it.
Remove the lid from the cabinet.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the right, go to the end of the couch and hang a left, go to the table on the right where the vase is.
Put the lid on the table to the right of the vase.
